  { q: "Does dynamic pricing really increase Airbnb revenue?", a: "Yes, by 27% on average. Listings using dynamic pricing tools earn $2,558/month compared to $2,020/month for those with static pricing. Dynamic pricing captures demand spikes during events, weekends, and peak seasons that static pricing misses." },
