          </ul>

          <p>That's a 4.5x difference between the top 10% and median. The question isn't whether Toronto Airbnb is profitable. It's whether you're doing what the top performers do.</p>

          <h2 id="revenue-tiers">Revenue Tiers: Where Do You Fit?</h2>
          <p>Based on our analysis, here's where Toronto 2-bedroom listings fall:</p>

